\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Thank you very much for submitting your manuscript "Axial and Radial Forces of Cross-bridges Depend on Lattice Spacing" for review by PLoS Computational Biology. Your manuscript was fully evaluated by the PLoS Computational Biology Editorial Team and in this case, also by 3 independent peer reviewers. The reviewers appreciated the attention to an important problem, and all three agree with me that your paper could be a major and lasting contribution to muscle biophysics. However, the raised some substantial questions about the manuscript as it currently stands, though their major concerns were primarily matters of presentation. In general, I think you will find all three reviewers' comments constructive and helpful. While your manuscript cannot be accepted in its present form, I am very willing to consider a revised version in which the issues raised by the reviewers have been adequately addressed. We cannot, of course, promise publication at that time, but i do look forward to}{\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
