\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Very much so. It has now received such attention.}{\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch TODO: I changed/checked the text for consistent use of "extensional spring" where we meant just that, and not "linear spring".}{\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
